  <br />
  <p><i><strong>Can I get cash back for the unused portion of my SugarDeal?</strong></i></p>
  No. Well, not unless required by law, anyways.
  <br /><br />
  <p><i><strong>Can I apply my SugarDeal over multiple visits to the redeeming business?</strong></i></p>
  No. Go wild and enjoy your deal to the full.
  <br /><br />
  <p><i><strong>Can my SugarDeal cover tax or gratuities?</strong></i></p>
  No. As a side note, SugarSave endorses generous tipping practices.
  <br /><br />
  <p><i><strong>Can I combine the value of my SugarDeal with other offers or coupons?</strong></i></p>
  Not unless specifically stated.
  <br /><br />
  <p><i><strong>When will my SugarDeal expire?</strong></i></p>
  Every SugarDeal will include a plainly-stated expiration date in the Crucial Deal Details. This date will also appear on your printed SugarDeal.
